      "author": "magnitus99",
      "description": "## Summary\n- Add guarded RAG indexing through a single scheduler for manual, automatic, and file-event updates.\n- Add performance backoff for slow batches and event loop lag before pausing indexing.\n- Default new vector stores to IndexedDB while preserving existing JSON vector stores.\n\n## Verification\n- npm ci\n- npm run lint\n- npm run typecheck\n- npm run test\n- npm run review -- --tag 1.0.15\n- npm run build\n- npm run review -- --tag 1.0.15 --built\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/magnitus99/Superpower-Inside/compare/1.0.14...1.0.15",
